{"tid":1374810,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"今日唔好再嗌「林鄭下台」","createTime":"2019-07-28T01:26:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T07:44:07.000Z","uid":112901,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9c75dfdc7b43926d4a6f74dcbc289539ba252b35","tid":1374810,"uid":112901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T01:26:08.000Z","msg":"反送中運動發展到今日，反緊嘅已經唔再係單單一條例，而係成個制度<br />\n<br />\n政治管治失效，而官員無需問責；警察濫權，市民無從追究。最仆街嘅係，依家已經猖狂到警黑合作，鏡頭底下犯法都奈佢哋唔何<br />\n<br />\n而因為呢個濕鳩政府，有人受傷，有人被捕，有人無家可歸、流亡海外，甚至有人選擇以死明志<br />\n<br />\n所以，林鄭只係下個台，對得住佢哋？更何況下台之後，如果制度依舊，上台嘅只會係另一個林鄭<br />\n<br />\n所以，就算唔係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港獨立</span></span>，至少都要<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">爭取雙真普選</span></span>"},{"pid":"6cb6274f1e849ae69fc8de71b9b8f57ca68471fc","tid":1374810,"uid":183344,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T01:29:47.000Z","msg":"啱呀，麻煩各位巴絲唔好再嗌呢四隻字，跛腳鴨政府以後乜鳩惡法都推唔到對香港人其實仲好"},{"pid":"c11fba3ef1bc1e866fa698654fb30753f7eb470e","tid":1374810,"uid":115041,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T01:34:00.000Z","msg":"一定要香港獨立！"},{"pid":"ff4d8d38a24640e2b6848ee751caa12ece822ad1","tid":1374810,"uid":112901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T01:34:25.000Z","msg":"認同請分享"},{"pid":"5b8468a4aeb77dd9587805deb71ee0e4be5a9ff6","tid":1374810,"uid":34415,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T01:36:23.000Z","msg":"我要真普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"310d114dd5ef650aadabd77516a2f3a885f6a238","tid":1374810,"uid":112901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T01:37:38.000Z","msg":"亦都唔好嗌林女士下台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a40c62d61262589c76c418d1c3d588c2f9e1c1c","tid":1374810,"uid":112901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T01:37:50.000Z